<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Snagajob</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrapper case-study snagajob">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Snagajob</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">One brand&nbsp;<br />to rule them all</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Hourly Jobs Search Application</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We redesigned the mobile apps for Snagajob, helping connect hourly workers with employers who need them.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded orange">
      <div class="container row between">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Make piecemeal into a whole meal
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            We improved both brand consistency and communication between product, design, and development.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            A top to bottom refresh
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            We went deeper than just the app screens. We uncovered process problems and helped Snagajob get back on course.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Employee Research</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">App Redesign</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Pattern Library</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">UX Process Consulting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Unifying and updating the app design</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Snagajob offers two apps — one for Job Seekers and one for Employers — for both Android and iOS. We refreshed and unified the designs for all four, creating a more holistic ecosystem.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl snagajob-apps">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile black shadow sr-left absolute">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/unify-mobile3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile black shadow sr-bottom">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/unify-mobile2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile black shadow sr-right absolute">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/unify-mobile1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top orange overflow-bottom">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Multiple operating systems</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            For both apps, we delivered compatible iOS and Android mockups, bringing the suite up to speed with iOS and Material Design standards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row snagajob-os">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile black shadow sr-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/os-mobile1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile-ios black shadow sr-right absolute-bottom">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/os-mobile2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded gray">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl snagajob-consistency">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile black shadow sr-stagger-left absolute">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/consistency-mobile1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile black shadow sr-stagger-left absolute">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/consistency-mobile2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile black shadow sr-stagger-left absolute">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/consistency-mobile3.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile black shadow sr-stagger-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
                <img src="./images/work/snagajob/consistency-mobile4.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column order-top-xs half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">All about the follow-through</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              We gave the employer app its own look, but kept the patterns and design building blocks the same, helping reinforce a consistent brand experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row dark-gray">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Looking at the bigger picture</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We conducted interviews with the client&rsquo;s internal teams and provided recommendations on workflow involving UX designers, product managers, engineers, and marketing reps.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column half-md hide-overflow">
        <img src="./images/work/snagajob/laptop-website.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image full-height">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded gray">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <img src="./images/work/snagajob/dev.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left">
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column order-top-xs half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Streamlined process from design to dev</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              In any united family of apps, the smooth handoff from mockups to development is key. We provided documentation in addition to a walkthrough of Sketch to Zeplin for the cleanest process possible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded orange">
      <div class="inner-block row">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <img src="./images/work/snagajob/icons.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-reveal">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
